                "invention-title": [
                    "Microgravity efficient steam generation and separation integrated device",
                    "一种微重力高效蒸汽发生分离一体器"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of steam generators, in particular to a microgravity efficient steam generation and separation integrated device which comprises a steam generation tank and a steam separation tank, the steam separation tank is located above the steam generation tank, one end of the steam generation tank is communicated with the steam separation tank through a steam outlet pipe, and the other end of the steam generation tank is communicated with the steam separation tank through a water return pipe. A tube plate and a plurality of heat exchange tubes are arranged in the steam generation tank, two ends of each heat exchange tube are inserted into the tube plate, a working medium inlet for a working medium to enter is formed in the upper end of the steam generation tank, a working medium outlet is formed in the lower end of the steam generation tank, a gas baffle is arranged at an inlet of the steam separation tank, and a steam outlet is formed in the upper end of the steam separation tank. Working media are condensed outside the pipe, water directly absorbs heat in the pipe to form high-temperature water mist and water vapor, the water mist and the water vapor are separated in the vapor separation tank, efficient heat exchange in the pipe and efficient condensation outside the pipe are achieved, the comprehensive heat exchange efficiency is improved, and the overall process of a heat pump unit is simplified."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及蒸汽发生器技术领域，具体为一种微重力高效蒸汽发生分离一体器，包括蒸汽发生罐和蒸汽分离罐，蒸汽分离罐位于蒸汽发生罐的上方，蒸汽发生罐的一端通过出汽管与蒸汽分离罐连通，另一端通过回水管与蒸汽分离罐连通，蒸汽发生罐内设有管板及多个换热管，多个所述换热管的两端插装在所述管板上，蒸汽发生罐的上端设有供工质进入的工质进口，下端设有工质出口，蒸汽分离罐的入口处设有挡气板，蒸汽分离罐的上端设有蒸汽出口。工质在管外冷凝，水在管内直接通过吸热形成高温水雾和水蒸气，水雾和水蒸气在蒸汽分离罐中发生分离，实现了管内高效换热、管外高效冷凝，提升了综合换热效率，精简了热泵机组整体流程。"
                }
            ]
